ed="T" n="0895c15"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0895c15"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>南嶽山<persName key="A008817">全玼</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0895c16"/><persName key="A008817">釋全玼</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000011893">餘杭</placeName>人也，入<placeName key="PL000000011848">徑山</placeName><anchor xml:id="beg0895sgsz19"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0895sgsz19"/><persName key="A010583">法濟大師</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0895c17"/>求剃染<ptr type="glossary" target="#g30"/>。稟質強渥，且耐飢寒。諸所參尋，略<lb
ed="T" n="0895c18"/>得周遍，乃隱<placeName key="PL000000028928">衡嶽</placeName>中立<anchor xml:id="beg0895sgsz21"/>草<anchor xml:id="end0895sgsz21"/>庵。木食<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1479"/>㵎飲，結<lb
ed="T" n="0895c19"/>軟草為衣，伏臘不易。有贈<persName key="A008817">玼</persName>詩云：「窠居<lb
ed="T" n="0895c20"/>過後更何人？傳得如來法印真。昨日<placeName key="PL000000028929">祝融峯</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0895c21"/>下見，草衣便是雪山身。」此太常<persName key="A009925">孫渥</persName>舊相南<lb
ed="T" n="0895c22"/>遷有作，事詳<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>高僧傳云。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0895c2301"><lb
ed="T" n="0895c23"/>系曰：草衣在<placeName key="PL000000028928">南嶽</placeName>炎方，壯年即可，未知衰<lb
ed="T" n="0895c24"/>老徙居幽朔耐否？如能，則上上根勝士也。</p>
